import React from 'react'; const About = () => { const stats = [ { number: '25+', label: 'Years of Experience' }, { number: '50+', label: 'Specialized Doctors' }, { number: '10000+', label: 'Happy Patients' }, { number: '24/7', label: 'Emergency Care' } ]; const values = [ { title: 'Patient-Centered Care', description: 'We prioritize our patients\' needs and well-being above all else.', icon: ( ) }, { title: 'Medical Excellence', description: 'We maintain the highest standards of medical care and treatment.', icon: ( ) }, { title: 'Innovation', description: 'We continuously adopt the latest medical technologies and practices.', icon: ( ) }, { title: 'Community Focus', description: 'We are committed to serving and improving our community\'s health.', icon: ( ) } ]; return (
{/* Hero Section */}

About Poliklinika

Providing exceptional healthcare services with compassion and expertise since 1998.

{/* Stats Section */}
{stats.map((stat) => (
{stat.number}
{stat.label}
))}
{/* Mission and Vision */}

Our Mission

To provide accessible, high-quality healthcare services to our community while maintaining the highest standards of medical excellence and patient care.

Our Vision

To be the leading healthcare provider in our region, known for our commitment to patient-centered care, medical innovation, and community well-being.

{/* Values Section */}

Our Core Values

{values.map((value) => (
{value.icon}

{value.title}

{value.description}

))}
{/* Facilities Section */}

Our Facilities

State-of-the-Art Equipment

We are equipped with the latest medical technology to ensure accurate diagnoses and effective treatments.

  • Advanced Imaging Systems
  • Modern Operating Rooms
  • Digital Medical Records

Comfortable Environment

Our facilities are designed to provide a comfortable and welcoming environment for our patients.

  • Spacious Waiting Areas
  • Private Consultation Rooms
  • Wheelchair Accessibility
); }; export default About;
